<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 21 Mar 2026 01:02:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于战争加剧通胀担忧，比特币难以守住 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-20/bitcoin-holding-at-70-000-as-iran-war-stokes-inflation-concerns</link><description>由于与伊朗战争相关的通胀担忧扰乱了市场，比特币周五一度跌破 70,000 美元，掩盖了美国加密货币监管新胜利。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ircsFMU9gnAw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 06:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-20/bitcoin-holding-at-70-000-as-iran-war-stokes-inflation-concerns</guid></item><item><title>Winklevosses 称 Gemini Exchange 裁员人数达到 30%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/winklevosses-says-jobs-cuts-at-gemini-exchange-reach-30</link><description>自年初以来，Gemini Space Station Inc. 裁员已达到约 30%，该加密货币交易所周四表示，正在部署人工智能工具以提高生产力。该公司去年亏损超过 5 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVKjfCCj1wqo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 22:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/winklevosses-says-jobs-cuts-at-gemini-exchange-reach-30</guid></item><item><title>数字信贷是加密货币财务公司杠杆的最新代号</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-19/digital-credit-is-the-latest-code-word-for-leverage-among-crypto-dats</link><description>数字资产国债越来越多地转向信贷市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNHrjc.FVWS8/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 21:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-19/digital-credit-is-the-latest-code-word-for-leverage-among-crypto-dats</guid></item><item><title>石油价格上涨冲击风险资产，比特币难以守住 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</link><description>由于中东能源基础设施再次遭受攻击，市场大范围抛售，比特币价格在一周多以来首次跌破 70,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKVCTkfcyAFQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</guid></item><item><title>前妻离婚后被指控盗窃 1.8 亿英镑比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</link><description>离婚后，一名丈夫指控前妻密谋窃取价值数百万美元的比特币和豪华手表，此案将考验英国民事法院如何对待数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVvrnnfg0iIU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</guid></item></channel></rss>